{"tid":731953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★「 梅林」午餐肉被驗出獸藥殘餘　或致皮疹和腫脹","createTime":"2018-07-06T15:30:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T17:06:57.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"dad4cdc76c4b494f5b39dda8032fc54ddf4a60f0","tid":731953,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T15:30:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/642609/org/7f72f39c7daddea78b396d38794891ea.jpg/UajZt411bQCgr6BZFYkEtQqeiKc5VSvyAmr3swJq97M?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F642609%2Forg%2F7f72f39c7daddea78b396d38794891ea.jpg%2FUajZt411bQCgr6BZFYkEtQqeiKc5VSvyAmr3swJq97M%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=f3aa548d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n消費者委員會（消委會）測試 25 款午餐肉及 8 款罐裝或瓶裝腸仔樣本，發現在「梅林」優質午餐肉（昌暉）樣本檢出磺胺類（sulfonamides）抗生素磺胺二甲嘧啶，含量達每公斤199.3 微克。消委會指磺胺二甲嘧啶是廣泛應用於獸醫學的藥物，對此藥敏感的人士，如果在食物中攝入磺胺二甲嘧啶殘餘，亦可能引發過敏反應，部份人食後會出現面部、口腔、舌頭出皮疹和腫脹。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>抗生素磺胺二甲嘧啶屬獸醫常用藥物</strong><br />\n消委會的測試發現，「梅林」優質午餐肉（昌暉）的樣本含有磺胺類（sulfonamides）抗生素磺胺二甲嘧啶，含量達每公斤199.3 微克。消委會指，一個60 公斤的成年人每日吃約15.1公斤（相等於38 罐）該樣本才達到相關限量，即一般情況下應不會因食用午餐肉而致超越攝入上限。惟仍要留意對該藥物的過敏反應，少數人在進食後會出現面部、口腔、舌頭出皮疹和腫脹。「梅林」優質午餐肉（昌暉）的代理商向消委會提供相關測試報告，表示有關產品沒有驗出磺胺二甲嘧啶。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/98035/%E6%B6%88%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83-%E6%A2%85%E6%9E%97-%E5%8D%88%E9%A4%90%E8%82%89%E8%A2%AB%E9%A9%97%E5%87%BA%E7%8D%B8%E8%97%A5%E6%AE%98%E9%A4%98-%E6%88%96%E8%87%B4%E7%9A%AE%E7%96%B9%E5%92%8C%E8%85%AB%E8%84%B9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F98035%2F%25E6%25B6%2588%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%259C%2583-%25E6%25A2%2585%25E6%259E%2597-%25E5%258D%2588%25E9%25A4%2590%25E8%2582%2589%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E9%25A9%2597%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%258D%25B8%25E8%2597%25A5%25E6%25AE%2598%25E9%25A4%2598-%25E6%2588%2596%25E8%2587%25B4%25E7%259A%25AE%25E7%2596%25B9%25E5%2592%258C%25E8%2585%25AB%25E8%2584%25B9&d=B3HrdDxKP23AUyn2VCpuXCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=7339f770\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/98035/%E6%B6%88%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83-%E6%A2%85%E6%9E%97-%E5%8D%88%E9%A4%90%E8%82%89%E8%A2%AB%E9%A9%97%E5%87%BA%E7%8D%B8%E8%97%A5%E6%AE%98%E9%A4%98-%E6%88%96%E8%87%B4%E7%9A%AE%E7%96%B9%E5%92%8C%E8%85%AB%E8%84%B9</a>"},{"pid":"b7c6b1d9a9161f8d3da2573b055c4fe2d68e2299","tid":731953,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T16:38:58.000Z","msg":"獸藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8beda6db2aa7473415cf80e9314d473dd28afb3","tid":731953,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T16:39:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/07/003949_3d7199133ab81123759851ae1fea4b91.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F07%2F003949_3d7199133ab81123759851ae1fea4b91.png&h=3e57a81b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea71be05c7c2fc065ff089f1926b42b757411e4a","tid":731953,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T16:47:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.parknshop.com/medias/sys_master/front/prd/8882635767838.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.parknshop.com%2Fmedias%2Fsys_master%2Ffront%2Fprd%2F8882635767838.jpg&h=504620a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.parknshop.com/medias/sys_master/front/prd/8799470419998.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.parknshop.com%2Fmedias%2Fsys_master%2Ffront%2Fprd%2F8799470419998.jpg&h=21b6751c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n緊係買來路貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n回帶西<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/red.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7678df2398a91b5d63d346f9d1ef8df633760